        <div id="description">
        	<h3>Course Description</h3>
            <p>This course takes all the skills and knowledge that students have obtained in the NMPD program and places them into groups to form their own production company. Learners will be simulated in real life work environments where they will learn how to communicate effectively to present a project or fulfill a task. This course mainly focuses on improving communication skills, teamwork, reliability and presentation delivery. </p>
            <p><strong>Course Credit:</strong> 3.0 per semester</p>
        </div>		